						<summary>

						<p>Mutilated hero-stone lying on the compound of the Śiva temple.</p>						

						<p>16th century A.D.</p>						

						<p>This inscription may be assigned to the 16th century A.D. on palaeographcal grounds.</p>						

						<p>Damaged. Purport is not clear. However, it refers to the setting up of the herostone on which this inscription is engraved.</p>						

						</summary>
